* {{ill|Tachibana Shrine (Mobara)|ja|橘樹神社 (茂原市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana Shrine (Mobara)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Mobara|Mobara, Chiba]], [[:en:Chiba Prefecture|Chiba Prefecture]]. Said to have been founded by {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ヤマトタケル}}. It is an {{ill|Enshrined deity of Engishiki|ja|延喜式神名帳|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enshrined deity of Engishiki|13=User:Immanuelle/Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=}} listed shrine, recognized as the [[:en:Ninomiya|Second Shrine (Ninomiya)]] of [[:en:Kazusa Province|Kazusa Province]], also known as Tachibana Shrine. After the Meiji era, it held the Rank of {{ill|Prefectural Shrine|ja|県社|lt=Ken-sha|1=Modern_system_of_ranked_Shinto_shrines#Metropolitan_and_Prefectural_Shrines|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prefectural Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 近代社格制度}} under the modern shrine Ranking system. It enshrines {{ill|Tachibanahime-no-Mikoto|lt=Tachibanahime-no-Mikoto|lt=Princess Ototachibana|ja|弟橘媛|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Princess Ototachibana|qq=}}.
* {{ill|Tachibana Shrine (Yokohama)|ja|橘樹神社 (横浜市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana Shrine (Yokohama)|qq=}} - Located in {{ill|Tennōchō, Hodogaya Ward, Yokohama|ja|保土ケ谷区天王町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tennōchō, Hodogaya Ward, Yokohama|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, [[:en:Yokohama|Yokohama]], [[:en:Kanagawa Prefecture|Kanagawa Prefecture]]. Also known as "Tennō-sama."
* {{ill|Tachibana Shrine (Kawasaki City)|ja|橘樹神社 (川崎市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana Shrine (Kawasaki City)|qq=}} - Located in {{ill|Shimoguchi, Takatsu Ward, Kawasaki|ja|高津区子母口|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimoguchi, Takatsu Ward, Kawasaki|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, [[:en:Kawasaki, Kanagawa|Kawasaki]], Kanagawa Prefecture, in the former {{ill|Tachibana District, Musashi Province|ja|武蔵国橘樹郡|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana District, Musashi Province|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}.
* {{nihongo|'''[[:en:Tachibana Shrine|Tachibana Shrine]]'''|橘夫人厨子|Tachibana-fujin no zushi}}, A non-Shinto shrine found at [[Hōryū-ji]]
